header.gameNote: NCAA Women's Championship pres. by Capital One - River Walk Region - Semifinal

videos.headline: Bueckers finds Edwards for the jumper
videos.description: Paige Bueckers looks to her left and finds the open Aaliyah Edwards for the easy jumper.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Bueckers finds Edwards for the jumper) 2021/03/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: Clark banks in the tough 3
videos.description: Iowa's Caitlin Clark banks in the tough 3-pointer from the left wing for her first basket of the day.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Clark banks in the tough 3) 2021/03/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: Bueckers gets the offensive rebound and bucket
videos.description: Paige Bueckers hauls in the offensive board then puts in the sweet floater in the lane.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Bueckers gets the offensive rebound and bucket) 2021/03/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: Clark dances on defender, drops dime to Czinano for layup
videos.description: Iowa's Caitlin Clark shows off the handles then throws the perfect bounce pass to Monika Czinano for the easy lay-in.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Clark dances on defender, drops dime to Czinano for layup) 2021/03/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: Williams caps off 18-point first half with a 3
videos.description: UConn's Christyn Williams swishes home the 3, giving her eighteen points in the first half.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Williams caps off 18-point first half with a 3) 2021/03/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: Excellent Iowa passing leads to the easy layup
videos.description: Iowa shows off its ball movement as McKenna Warnock finds Monika Czinano for the easy layup.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Excellent Iowa passing leads to the easy layup) 2021/03/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: Bueckers drops dime to Edwards for the layup
videos.description: UConn turns defense into offense as Paige Bueckers drops a dime to Aaliyah Edwards for the easy layup.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Bueckers drops dime to Edwards for the layup) 2021/03/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: Clark buries a 3 to end the third quarter
videos.description: Caitlin Clark takes one step to her left and drains the 3-pointer right at the third-quarter buzzer.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Clark buries a 3 to end the third quarter) 2021/03/027 ESHEET

videos.headline: Bueckers knocks down two huge 3-pointers
videos.description: Paige Bueckers responds to Iowa twice as she drains two huge 3-pointers.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Bueckers knocks down two huge 3-pointers) 2021/03/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: Williams ices Iowa with sweet scoop layup
videos.description: UConn's Christyn Williams drives down the lane and flips in a sweet scoop layup, putting the Huskies up 17 late.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Williams ices Iowa with sweet scoop layup) 2021/03/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: Auriemma looks back at Bueckers after she taps him following a 3
videos.description: UConn's Anna Makurat knocks down the 3-pointer as Paige Bueckers celebrates with coach Auriemma following the shot.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Auriemma looks back at Bueckers after she taps him following a 3) 2021/03/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: UConn's Williams, Westbrook credit total total team effort in win over Iowa
videos.description: Holly Rowe catches up with Christyn Williams and Evina Westbrook after UConn's 92-72 win over Iowa to advance to the Elite Eight.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCW Interview (UConn's Williams, Westbrook credit total total team effort in win over Iowa) 2021/03/27

videos.headline: Bueckers, Williams outduel Clark as UConn advances to the Elite Eight
videos.description: Paige Bueckers scores 18 while Christyn Williams drops 27 of her own as UConn outduels Caitlin Clark and Iowa to advance to the Elite Eight.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCW Highlight (Bueckers, Williams outduel Clark as UConn advances to the Elite 8) 2021/03/27 ESHEET SOTFULL
